data.description:
Welcome to 3320 W CABALLERO DR, Eloy, AZ 85131! Built in 2013, this delightful 3 bed, 2 bath double-wide home offers 1,569 sqft of comfortable living space on an expansive 13,442 sqft lot, providing ample room for your family and activities.

Situated on a quarter-acre lot with mature fruit trees—blackberries, oranges, apricots, lemons, and limes—creating a lush, private oasis ideal for family gatherings and BBQs. The backyard, with its North-South exposure, is perfect for basking in the warm Arizona sun. The outdoor space is enhanced by pavers and a covered patio area featuring a tile countertop, perfect for enjoying outdoor dining and entertaining.

Step inside to a spacious, light-filled open-concept layout seamlessly integrating living, dining, and a modern gourmet kitchen The kitchen, a culinary enthusiast's dream, features modern appliances, ample counter space, and a large islandideal for savoring morning coffee or hosting lively dinner parties. The home offers both a living room and a family room, providing versatile spaces for relaxation and entertainment.

The interior boasts vinyl wood-like and tile vinyl flooring complemented by newer carpeting, adding both style and comfort to the home. Retreat to peaceful bedrooms, including a master suite with an en-suite bathroom and generous closet space, offering a tranquil start to your day with the gentle Arizona sun streaming through the windows.

One of the fantastic features of this property is its affordability, with annual taxes totaling only $552a true benefit for homeowners.

Conveniently located in the heart of Eloy, AZ, this home provides easy access to amenities, shopping, dining, and nearby attractions. Embrace the Arizona lifestyle, whether it's desert adventures, exploring local parks, or immersing in the vibrant community.

With its convenient commute to neighboring cities and major highways, this home offers both tranquility and accessibility. Seize the opportunity to make 3320 W CABALLERO DR your forever home in beautiful Eloy, AZ. Contact us today to envision your Arizona adventure!
